exchange_rate_etl/
├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py        # App and database initialization
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── __init__.py    # Models module initialization
│   │   ├── exchange_rate.py  # ExchangeRate model definition
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── __init__.py    # Services module initialization
│   │   ├── etl_service.py # Main ETL pipeline script
│   ├── routes/            # Flask routes
│   └── templates/         # HTML templates for Flask views
├── instance/              # Contains the SQLite database
│   └── exchange_rates.db  # SQLite database file
├── validate_db.py         # Script to validate loaded data
├── test_db.py             # Script to verify table creation
├── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
└── README.md              # Project documentation
